headline: S&P 500 Gains and Losses Today: Kroger Stock Soars, Accenture Shares Drop
summary: The S&P 500 slid 0.2% on Friday, June 20, wrapping up the shortened trading week as investors mulled the implications of the ongoing conflict in the Middle East.
